title: Meme Competition
body:
Utilize 1,000 PINT & ~ 0.0285 ETH from the war-chest to fund a meme contest.

Purpose: Grow interest in PINT via memes, using the PINT as incentive for people to participate.

General Rules:
2 week submission period
Users can submit multiple Memes
Memes must use $PINT and #WenRug hashtags and links to the Tweets posted in the PINT Telegram channel
Informal voting in the VIP room will narrow the selection to the top 10 Memes
A snapshot proposal will rank the top 10
Top 5 will be rewarded as follows:
1: 500 pint
2: 200 pint
3: 100 pint
4: 100 pint
5: 100 pint

Rewards will be sent using an ETH gas basefee of 57 gwei (~0.0057 ETH per Tx) to reduce the cost of running the contest.

Total Budget: 1,000 PINT + ~.0285 ETH
choices: No - do not use the funds
